## Feedback and issues

If you run into a problem or have an idea for a new type of fix, please open an issue on the GitHub repository with:

- Your Thunderbird version
- Your operating system
- A short description of what you were doing
- Any error messages or screenshots that might help

Thank you for trying WayneWright and helping improve it.
